explanation:
Characteristic feature of gallstone ileus is Rigler's triad :

Incomplete or complete small bowel obstruction; 
Gas in biliary tree; 
Ectopic gallstone.

Information is this question are :-
	1) Exposure to textile industry; 
	2) Reticulo-nodular pattern in lower lung zone; 
	3) Loss of definition of heart border and diphragm; 
	4) Small pleural effusion. 
	​All these suggest the diagnosis of asbestosis.
